reviews: Great product. I've had it for 2 years and it's still holding up great.

These shirts are sized big. I usually take an XL but the XL in this shirt was pretty big but hopefully will shrink in the washer/dryer. Otherwise very good quality and the pocket is strong enough to hold things.
Awesome product that has to be every carpenters favorite sqaure do to the inside scribe cut outs.
Quality made product that holds up to the daily tasks it was bought for. Great little edc knife on your keyring.

review_title: Cheap quality hat thats great for anyone
reviews: Hat stretches to fit your head. Great product. Im an apprentice carpenter and it holds up very well on the job. Holds up for easily half a year for like $12? Lots of colors to choose for different days of the week too which I like. Can't be beat imo.

review_title: Great water bottle for all ! ðŸ™‚
reviews: Great water bottle that holds lots. I've dropped it plenty of times and it barely has marks on it and holds up great. Nothing bad to say.

review_title: Can't beat this watch for the price!
reviews: Can't beat this watch for the price. I like it because I work in trades and if it takes a beating I can just order another one. Awesome watch for hands on working people.

review_title: Durable and has a slot for a lock if you want to lock it up.
reviews: I was expecting this to be lower quality with the price being so low but it's great to be honest! Very solid and holds all of my carpentry tools that I don't take in my belt. It's compact and fits great in the trunk/backseat.
This saves your wrist alot of extra motion. Holds all extra bits too in the back compartment which is great.

review_title: Durable materials. Small size, good for finish work.

reviews: I bought this on May 17, 2017 and it still is in great condition. Nothing bad to say about this product whatsoever.
